- cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems): The paper proposes an auction mechanism that involves multiple agents (publishers, advertisers, and viewers) and their interactions. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper discusses digital ads and their impact on viewer experience, which is relevant to multimedia and user experience research.
